text: Businesses give lukewarm welcome to Corbyn's left-wing top team New Labour front bench includes a shadow chancellor who aims to nationalise banks After a series of resignations from the senior ranks in the wake of Jeremy Corbyn's victory, the official Opposition now includes numerous newcomers Photo: Getty Images
